start¶

Direction of Progress: start.py –> questionNumInput.py

  • This file is the first part of the program. Program will run by running this file

  • Corresponds to the main screen of the program

  • Enter the names of students in ‘nameList.txt’ without spaces on each line

  • Prepare unmarked test papers and marked students’ test paper files
